<p>What about the following sandbox request is causing the 10400 response? The error indicates "Order total is missing." Yet according to PayPal documentation, PAYMENTREQUEST_0_AMT is the order total.</p>  <p>Request:</p>  <pre><code>METHOD=SetExpressCheckout VERSION=97 RETURNURL=https://localhost:8443/return CANCELURL=https://localhost:8443/cancel PAYMENTREQUEST_0_PAYMENTACTION=AUTHORIZATION PAYMENTREQUEST_0_AMT=0 PAYMENTREQUEST_0_CURRENCYCODE=USD L_BILLINGTYPE0=MerchantInitiatedBilling </code></pre>  <p>Response:</p>  <pre><code>TIMESTAMP=2015-10-02T16:49:02Z CORRELATIONID=19e446a3f630 ACK=Failure VERSION=3.0 BUILD=000000 L_ERRORCODE0=10400 L_SHORTMESSAGE0=Transaction refused because of an invalid argument. See additional error messages for details. L_LONGMESSAGE0=Order total is missing. L_SEVERITYCODE0=Error </code></pre>